{"tid":1656272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【要不是美國政府照顧你們中國】9月豬肉價再上漲七成 中國急購美國豬肉救急","createTime":"2019-10-15T13:38:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T15:22:57.000Z","uid":117837,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6d2296d8883882618ab535b64ff2ea1b60501ba8","tid":1656272,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"【9月豬肉價再上漲七成】<br />\n【中國急購美國豬肉救急?】<br />\n<br />\n中國通脹持續升溫，9月居民消費價格指數)按年升幅加快至3%，升幅創近6年新高，而最令民眾憂慮的，是上個月豬肉價格同比上漲近七成。<br />\n另一方面，中國外交部發言人耿爽表示，已向美國購買大批豬肉和其他糧食，而且採購步伐還會加快。<br />\n內地金融界擔心，購買外國糧食需要龐大外匯，擔心中國外匯儲備會進一步萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=510269156438055&amp;_rdr\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D510269156438055%26_rdr&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLC3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=93b64e37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/watch/?v=510269156438055&amp;_rdr</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/07dewb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F07dewb7.png&h=1a2013af&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4076ebe005923a0c895e444bf8bd3ba6a7e13d87","tid":1656272,"uid":117837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:40:05.000Z","msg":"陰功咯<br />\n豬肉都要靠美國佬<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c525840efc7a6c646ca9bad1e90bd130c35347","tid":1656272,"uid":73856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:40:20.000Z","msg":"唔繼續幫襯俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922d514801aa8e1cfa604c7fdd77cc623d3de7f4","tid":1656272,"uid":128489,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:40:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3f6a40cfa0c888cc798b39629234c86f1d39e0d4","tid":1656272,"uid":117837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T13:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" cla